value:
I've always been adorable, but this
outfit makes me even cuter! I can't
wait to see what my brother thinks.

We don't have festivals as fun as this
back where I'm from. The outside
world really is amazing!

You wanna know what's in this
egg? Hmm, maybe I'll tell you... Just
kidding! I don't know either!

Look! Now that I'm a rabbit, nobody
can catch me! Why? Because I can
hop higher than anybunny. Hehe!

Hehe, oh big brother. Did you really
think I wouldn't find you? These big
bunny ears can hear you anywhere!

Bounce bounce! I'm not just hiding
cute eggs; I bring spring greetings
from $Nf too!

Amazing! I'm still a genius, even when
I'm a rabbit.

Hippity-hop! You can't catch me that
easily!

Huh? That didn't go as great as I'd
expected. Did I trip on an egg?
Now it will always feel like spring!

Ta-da! It's Delthea! Aren't I just the
cutest rabbit? I'm going to make this
spring festival so much fun!

You absolutely made the right choice
when you invited me for the spring
festival, $Nu!$k$pI had so much fun! And I was able to
make a lot of people smile while
doing it! Even my brother had fun.$k$pI've spent most of my life wishing I
could go to a festival as wonderful
as this.$k$pAll I could do back home was
practice magic, with only my brother
to talk to. I was so bored!$k$pBut there are so many exciting things
to see and do outside my village,
including these great festivals!$k$pI want to experience so many more
things. I can't wait to see what my
next adventure will be!
やーあ！
春だよっ
うわあっ
もー、最悪…
The hop never stops!
Fear the rabbit!
Am I cute or what?
Springtime fun!
No fair...
んー？
Didn't think I had such a cute side, did you?
Hey! Oh, come on... Is that any way to treat a lady?
Spring is my favorite season! Lively and romantic.
Did you see Luthier's costume? He looks amazing!
Why are rabbits always hiding their eggs? And how many eggs are they laying?!
Rabbits are cute and all, but I've always thought of them as food, not family.
Come on, the festival isn't over yet. There's still so much to see and do!
Lovely weather!
Where to?
Hippity hop!
